ZH: 今生今世我们都会一直相爱。
EN: We will love each other forever in this life.

ZH: 今生今世我都会珍惜与你在一起的时光。
EN: I will cherish the time we spend together in this life.

ZH: 今生今世，我只愿成为你的唯一。
EN: In this life, I only want to be your one and only.

ZH: 今生今世，我愿意守护你一生一世。
EN: I am willing to protect you in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我们的爱永远不会改变。
EN: Our love will never change in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我只属于你。
EN: In this life and the next, I belong only to you.

ZH: 今生今世，你都是我的唯一。
EN: You are my one and only in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我都会陪伴在你的身边。
EN: In this life and the next, I will always be by your side.

ZH: 今生今世，我们都会永远在一起。
EN: We will be together forever in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我永远不会放手。
EN: I will never let go in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，你是我最爱的人。
EN: You are the one I love the most in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我们将永远心连心。
EN: We will be heart to heart forever in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我的心只属于你。
EN: My heart belongs only to you in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我们的爱会永不熄灭。
EN: Our love will never die out in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我只想与你共度余生。
EN: In this life and the next, I only want to spend my life with you.

ZH: 今生今世，我都会珍惜和你在一起的每一刻。
EN: I will cherish every moment we spend together in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我将永远记得你的笑容。
EN: I will always remember your smile in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我会一直宠爱你。
EN: I will always spoil and cherish you in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我会永远守护你的梦想。
EN: I will forever protect your dreams in this life and the next.

ZH: 今生今世，我都会永远爱着你。
EN: I will always love you in this life and the next.
